Package si.ijs.kt.clus.util.tools.optimization

Class OptimizationProblem.OptimizationParameter

java.lang.Object
si.ijs.kt.clus.util.tools.optimization.OptimizationProblem.OptimizationParameter
Enclosing class:
OptimizationProblem
public static class OptimizationProblem.OptimizationParameter extends Object
Parameters for optimization algorithm. Predictions for rules and other base function and true values for all the instances of data. The default prediction is used, if no other rule covers the instance. See m_RulePred and m_TrueVal for what the indices mean.
